| Issue | Original | Fixed |
|-------|----------|-------|
| Extra Promise wrapper | `async function` | Plain `function` |
| Timer leak | `Promise.race` leaves timer running | `clearTimeout()` on settlement |
| Unhandled rejection | Original promise may reject later | Documented limitation; see note below |
| Error type | `reject('timeout')` | `reject(new TimeoutError())` |
| Input safety | No validation | Type & range checks for `ms` and
